main event: Two witnesses observed a round object that was green and red, which hovered, dived down, and then stopped completely for about 15 minutes.
interesting points: The object appeared to glow and then become less bright, as noted by a witness using binoculars., The incident took place on the night of August 1, 1966., One of the witnesses was 14 years old and seemed to have seen something significant., There was no physical evidence found at the scene., The conclusion of the report suggested the object was likely an aircraft.
sighted object: one round object that was green and red
witness description: two witnesses with one being a 14-year-old boy
